         <li>
            <p>Replacing the top part of the mixing arm and/or the outer scraper arm:</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>Unscrew the adjustment screws (6 &amp; 11) far enough for the spring (8) and
                     plug bolt (4) to be pulled out.</li>
                  <li>Remove the insertable sheet (10).</li>
                  <li>Remove the feather key (7) by moving the adjusting rings (5 &amp; 9) to the
                     side.</li>
                  <li>Pull the top part of the mixing arm (14) out of the rotor case (12).</li>
                  <li>To reassemble, complete the steps in reverse order.</li>
               </ul>
