         <li>
            <p>If replacing only the bottom part of the mixing arm (5 in image on the
                  right):</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>Remove the screws (3, 4), and remove the threaded plate (1).</li>
                  <li>The arm should be free.</li>
               </ul>
               <note type="note" id="note_ylh_wxr_lcc">
                  <p>Re-tighten the connections between the top part of the mixing arm and the
                     bottom part of the mixing arm after 5 hours of operating time.</p>
               </note>
