         <li>
            <p>Replacing the mixing arm bearings:</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>The mixing arm bearings (1) are bushings that are inserted into the drilled holes of the rotor, and into which the mixing arms are inserted.</li>
                  <li>The mixing arm bearings can only be replaced after the mixing arms have been
                     removed.</li>
               </ul>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_ip2_f1s_lcc">
